production controls is present but not foregrounded."],"overstated_risk_now":["The 'Engineering Leader' headline can pull the profile toward manager/executive interpretation instead of senior architect/player-coach fit.","Role-level skill inventories include broad people-management and executive-style terms that exceed the strongest evidence for this category.","Cloud/provider and compliance cues could be overread if they are left unqualified by delivered-scope wording."],"representation_priorities":["Re-anchor the headline and summary around AI architect / AI solution architect language backed by Commander-4 plus Seven.One architecture proof.","Move one Commander-4 architecture bullet into the opening summary or top role bullets so AI platform delivery is visible before generic leadership framing.","Add one greenfield architecture proof point from Daypaio and one stakeholder-translation proof point from Daypaio/Seven.One/Clary to balance the current modernization-heavy narrative.","Rebalance skills toward architecture outcomes and platform capabilities rather than a long tool list or generic management vocabulary."],"citations":["data/master-cv/role_metadata.json:3","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:71","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:27","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44","data/master-cv/roles/06_clary_icon.md:103","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:2","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:10"]},"curation_priorities":[{"priority_rank":1,"action":"Promote the upstream Seven.One architect-title framing into curated metadata as an evidenced alias or targeting variant.","why_now":"This is the cleanest way to close the title-family gap for an architect-led category without fabricating a title change.","target_files":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md","data/master-cv/role_metadata.json"],"source_refs":["docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:7","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:98","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:181","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:268","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:360"],"expected_category_impact":"Improves headline safety, title-family fit, and summary alignment for AI architect targeting.","citation":"Upstream STAR records repeatedly describe the current role with explicit architect-heavy framing."},{"priority_rank":2,"action":"Promote Daypaio greenfield platform-launch evidence and event-storming facilitation into higher-salience curated variants for architect targeting.","why_now":"The category explicitly rewards greenfield-plus-modernization range, and Daypaio is the best curated counterweight to Seven.One modernization.","target_files":["data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md","data/master-cv/role_metadata.json"],"source_refs":["docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:734"],"expected_category_impact":"Strengthens greenfield architecture, stakeholder workshop, and player-coach signals without relying only on the current role.","citation":"STAR record #9 adds stronger end-to-end architecture and market-launch framing than the current top-line representation."},{"priority_rank":3,"action":"Promote a curated Seven.One variant that explicitly ties AI platform work to architecture ownership, governance controls, and enterprise integration rather than search mechanics alone.","why_now":"Commander-4 is the strongest AI-specific proof and should carry more category weight than it currently does.","target_files":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md","data/master-cv/role_metadata.json"],"source_refs":["docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:360","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:268"],"expected_category_impact":"Improves AI architect fit by turning strong technical AI evidence into cleare